text: is a Prefectural Natural Park in Akita Prefecture, Japan. Established in 2004, the park spans the borders of the municipalities of Fujisato and Happō, and takes its name from the Shirakami-Sanchi. ==See also== * National Parks of Japan * Parks and gardens in Akita Prefecture ==References== Category:Parks and gardens in Akita Prefecture Category:Protected areas established in 2004 Category:2004 establishments in Japan Category:Fujisato, Akita Category:Happō, Akita
title: Akita Shirakami Prefectural Natural Park
